<bibRefCitation author="Miller and Lea" box="[645,886,1375,1401]" firstAuthor="Miller" pageId="153" pageNumber="154" refId="ref302113" refString="Miller, D. J. &amp; Lea, R. N. (1972) Guide to the coastal marine fishes of California. California Department of Fish and Game Fish Bulletin, 157." type="book" year="1972">Miller and Lea (1972)</bibRefCitation>
